title: Please help identify this font
content:
![](http://web.archive.org/web/20131019101335im_/http:/typophile.com/files/37fac9793947204dfd2404bdcaf4128c_6210.62924.png)

Please help identify the Europop logo font pictured :)
author: Brody Blue

comments.content: Thought it was very easy but as I was unable to spot a match, here are some similars: [Pirulen](http://web.archive.org/web/20131019101335/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/typodermic/pirulen) (probably the closest), [Bitsumishi](http://web.archive.org/web/20131019101335/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/cheapprofonts/bitsumishi-pro-v2), [Trivial](http://web.archive.org/web/20131019101335/http:/www.dafont.com/trivial.font), [Korataki](http://web.archive.org/web/20131019101335/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/typodermic/korataki)
